race.comment: TINKLEJAZZ (10) So You Think filly from former top race mare Fullazz on debut for the Archibald stable. Has shown ability in both trials and gets an economical run from the low barrier. Worthy contender. EXPLICIT (13) resumes after showing potential in three career starts. Since fitted with the two soft trials and will go back from the draw. Can run into the minor money. MILITANT (4) has shown enough at the trials to suggest he can run a big race on debut from the soft draw. Fellow debutant ONOMA (5) also has to be included despite the wide draw.
